### Manual Leaderboard API Tests
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001
@adminToken = YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### 2. Get All Leaderboards (Public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/manual-leaderboards?status=active&limit=10

### 3. Create Leaderboard (Admin Only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/manual-leaderboards/admin/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "title": "Weekly High Roller Challenge",
  "description": "Compete for the highest total wagers this week!",
  "prizePool": "$500",
  "startDate": "2026-05-01T00:00:00Z",
  "endDate": "2026-05-08T00:00:00Z",
  "prizes": [
    {
      "position": 1,
      "prizeAmount": "$250",
      "prizeDescription": "First Place Winner"
    },
    {
      "position": 2,
      "prizeAmount": "$150",
      "prizeDescription": "Second Place"
    },
    {
      "position": 3,
      "prizeAmount": "$100",
      "prizeDescription": "Third Place"
    }
  ]
}

### 4. Get Leaderboard Details (Public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/manual-leaderboards/LEADERBOARD_ID_HERE

### 5. Add Wager (Admin Only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/manual-leaderboards/admin/LEADERBOARD_ID_HERE/wagers
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "userId": "USER_ID_HERE",
  "amount": 1500.50,
  "notes": "Big win on slots"
}

### 6. Update Prize Distribution (Admin Only)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/manual-leaderboards/admin/LEADERBOARD_ID_HERE/prizes
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "prizes": [
    {
      "position": 1,
      "prizeAmount": "$300",
      "prizeDescription": "First Place - Updated"
    },
    {
      "position": 2,
      "prizeAmount": "$200",
      "prizeDescription": "Second Place - Updated"
    }
  ]
}

### 7. Export Leaderboard (Admin Only - JSON)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/manual-leaderboards/admin/LEADERBOARD_ID_HERE/export
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 8. Export Leaderboard (Admin Only - CSV)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/manual-leaderboards/admin/LEADERBOARD_ID_HERE/export?format=csv
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 9. Get User Total Wagers (Authenticated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/manual-leaderboards/LEADERBOARD_ID_HERE/user-total
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 10. Delete Leaderboard (Admin Only)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/manual-leaderboards/admin/LEADERBOARD_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
